50:00.000 --> 50:03.000
Oh, like you, Germany.

50:03.000 --> 50:08.000
How many times do I have to tell you, Julia, with a question you do?

50:08.000 --> 50:10.000
Do, do, do.

50:10.000 --> 50:15.000
Yes, do like you, Germany.

50:15.000 --> 50:16.000
No, no, no.

50:16.000 --> 50:18.000
Do you like Germany?

50:18.000 --> 50:20.000
Yes, I like.

50:20.000 --> 50:21.000
No, Julia.

50:21.000 --> 50:23.000
I'm not asking you.

50:23.000 --> 50:28.000
But you say to me, do you like Germany?

50:28.000 --> 50:29.000
Yes, I know.

50:29.000 --> 50:33.000
But I was trying to tell you the correct question in English.

50:33.000 --> 50:35.000
Oh, I see.

50:35.000 --> 50:38.000
And the answer is, yes, I do.

50:38.000 --> 50:40.000
I, too.

50:40.000 --> 50:41.000
I, too, what?

50:41.000 --> 50:44.000
Sorry. I, too.

50:44.000 --> 50:45.000
Thank you.

50:45.000 --> 50:48.000
Sit down, Julia. Thank you.

50:48.000 --> 50:49.000
Alba.

50:49.000 --> 50:51.000
Do you have a question?

50:51.000 --> 50:53.000
Yes, I do.

50:53.000 --> 50:55.000
Good. Please read it.

50:55.000 --> 50:58.000
