56:09.000 --> 56:11.000
Somebody here to save me.

56:11.000 --> 56:13.000
Oh, my leg.

56:20.000 --> 56:22.000
Flying is better.

56:24.000 --> 56:26.000
Unbelievable.

56:26.000 --> 56:27.000
Unbelievable.

56:27.000 --> 56:29.000
All right, all right.

56:29.000 --> 56:31.000
What a family.

56:31.000 --> 56:32.000
Unbelievable.

56:32.000 --> 56:34.000
