56:34.000 --> 56:37.000
Well, it is rather unbelievable.

56:38.000 --> 56:39.000
I know.

56:39.000 --> 56:40.000
Your mother started it.

56:40.000 --> 56:41.000
No, I didn't.

56:41.000 --> 56:43.000
How is the leg, Nancy?

56:43.000 --> 56:44.000
Does it hurt?

56:44.000 --> 56:45.000
Yes, it does.

56:45.000 --> 56:46.000
A lot.

56:46.000 --> 56:51.000
