56:51.000 --> 56:52.000
I'm sorry.

56:52.000 --> 56:53.000
My friend Marcus.

56:53.000 --> 56:56.000
I heard you the first time, but why are you telling us?

56:56.000 --> 56:59.000
Just wanted to make Nancy feel better.

56:59.000 --> 57:03.000
You think telling a story about some old codger losing his leg on a Tuesday

57:03.000 --> 57:05.000
