57:24.000 --> 57:25.000
I know.

57:25.000 --> 57:27.000
Nancy can stay with us a bit longer.

57:27.000 --> 57:29.000
That's a good idea, Heidi.

57:29.000 --> 57:35.000
I am very happy to have you in my house for a few days, and then I can put you on a flight to London.

57:35.000 --> 57:36.000
Maybe next week.

57:36.000 --> 57:38.000
Oh, but I couldn't.

57:38.000 --> 57:39.000
That's...

57:39.000 --> 57:40.000
That's decided then.

57:40.000 --> 57:41.000
But...

57:41.000 --> 57:42.000
No more discussion.

57:42.000 --> 57:44.000
That's organised then.

57:44.000 --> 57:45.000
Good.

57:45.000 --> 57:46.000
Come on, Heidi.

57:46.000 --> 57:48.000
Let's go and organise something to eat.

57:48.000 --> 57:52.000
I don't remember saying yes to dead leg to you.

57:52.000 --> 57:54.000
No.

57:54.000 --> 57:56.000
I didn't either, but he's very...

57:56.000 --> 57:57.000
German.

57:57.000 --> 57:58.000
He's very German.

57:58.000 --> 58:01.000
