58:01.000 --> 58:03.000
It's a good idea, Nancy.

58:03.000 --> 58:04.000
Don't you think?

58:04.000 --> 58:09.000
12 hours in that car with your leg bandaged is not a good idea.

58:09.000 --> 58:14.000
And I'm sure the two of you can have a nice time together.

58:14.000 --> 58:18.000
