58:36.000 --> 58:37.000
Me, too.

58:37.000 --> 58:38.000
It's a great idea.

58:38.000 --> 58:39.000
But...

58:39.000 --> 58:40.000
Jean, she's ready.

58:40.000 --> 58:41.000
Come on.

58:41.000 --> 58:44.000
Can Josie and I stay here with Nancy for another week?

58:44.000 --> 58:45.000
Of course.

58:45.000 --> 58:46.000
A nice idea.

58:46.000 --> 58:47.000
Cool.

58:47.000 --> 58:49.000
Then we can fly back together.

58:49.000 --> 58:50.000
But...

58:50.000 --> 58:51.000
But...

58:51.000 --> 58:52.000
What about me?

58:52.000 --> 58:55.000
You told me you never wanted to fly.

58:55.000 --> 58:56.000
Remember?

58:56.000 --> 58:57.000
Yes, but...

58:57.000 --> 59:01.000
Your three ladies can fly back with one of those cheap airlines.

59:01.000 --> 59:02.000
It's not expensive.

59:02.000 --> 59:03.000
Wonderful.

59:03.000 --> 59:05.000
What a lovely idea.

59:05.000 --> 59:07.000
I don't know how to thank you.

59:07.000 --> 59:09.000
I'm sure you can think of something, Mum.

59:09.000 --> 59:11.000
What do you mean, Josie?

59:11.000 --> 59:13.000
Nothing, Mum, nothing.

59:13.000 --> 59:15.000
Anyway, Pete.

59:15.000 --> 59:17.000
