01:00:44.000 --> 01:00:45.000
Sorry, Mum.

01:00:45.000 --> 01:00:49.000
Something about the three of you having a nice journey?

01:00:49.000 --> 01:00:50.000
Er...

01:00:50.000 --> 01:00:51.000
Nothing, Mum.

01:00:51.000 --> 01:00:53.000
You didn't, did you?

01:00:53.000 --> 01:00:54.000
I didn't.

01:00:54.000 --> 01:00:55.000
What?

01:00:55.000 --> 01:00:57.000
Where's that rat of yours?

01:00:57.000 --> 01:00:59.000
Oh, I'm not sure.

01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:01.000
Er, I think he's in a box.

01:01:01.000 --> 01:01:04.000
And where's the box, Josephine?

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:06.000
I think it, er...

01:01:06.000 --> 01:01:08.000
Maybe, er...

01:01:08.000 --> 01:01:11.000
In Dad's car, er...

01:01:11.000 --> 01:01:12.000
Maybe.

01:01:12.000 --> 01:01:13.000
Oh!

01:01:13.000 --> 01:01:18.000
Your father is going to get a very big shock when he gets home.

01:01:18.000 --> 01:01:22.000
