01:01:52.000 --> 01:01:56.000
Your dog needs a passport, sir, to show he's been inoculated.

01:01:56.000 --> 01:01:57.000
He's fine.

01:01:57.000 --> 01:02:01.000
He hasn't been near any strange dogs in Germany.

01:02:01.000 --> 01:02:04.000
But there are one or two strange people there.

01:02:04.000 --> 01:02:06.000
I'm sorry, sir. It's the law.

01:02:06.000 --> 01:02:10.000
Your dog will have to be put in quarantine for six months.

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:11.000
Six months?

01:02:11.000 --> 01:02:12.000
Oh, no.

01:02:12.000 --> 01:02:14.000
What's Nancy going to say when she gets home?

01:02:14.000 --> 01:02:15.000
She'll kill me.

01:02:15.000 --> 01:02:17.000
There must be something I can do.

01:02:17.000 --> 01:02:19.000
I'm sorry, sir.

01:02:19.000 --> 01:02:21.000
Can you bring your dog with me, sir?

01:02:24.000 --> 01:02:26.000
Problems with your breaks, sir?

01:02:26.000 --> 01:02:27.000
Uh...

01:02:27.000 --> 01:02:28.000
I...

01:02:28.000 --> 01:02:29.000
Uh...

01:02:49.000 --> 01:02:51.000
Oh, no!

